    <section id="overview">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-base-content mt-10 mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-base-300">1. 模板名称与用途</h2>
      <p class="mb-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-base-content/90">
        <strong>Help Center（<code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">help</code>）</strong>是 Baklib 为 Wiki 站点提供的帮助中心主题。它将知识库内容呈现为产品文档、FAQ 与操作指南，无需从零搭建文档站。核心能力包括：
      </p>
      <ul class="mb-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-base leading-relaxed text-base-content/90">
        <li><strong>三种首页布局</strong>：卡片式、FAQ 折叠列表、极简支持首页，可按站点需求在后台切换。</li>
        <li><strong>双栏内容页</strong>：主栏正文 + 右侧粘性侧栏（常见主题、标签云、联系支持）。</li>
        <li><strong>搜索与 AI 问答</strong>：关键词搜索、热门标签/关键词引导；站点开启 AI 搜索后，搜索页侧栏展示 AI 问答面板。</li>
        <li><strong>页面工具</strong>：复制 Markdown、在 ChatGPT/Claude 中打开、MCP 安装命令、连接 Cursor/VS Code。</li>
        <li><strong>读者反馈</strong>：叶子页面底部提供「有帮助 / 无帮助」反馈入口。</li>
        <li><strong>多语言</strong>：内置 7 种语言的运行时 UI 与主题编辑器文案。</li>
        <li><strong>品牌可视化</strong>：静态页 <code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">/s/brand</code> 展示完整设计 token 与组件示例。</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section id="structure">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-base-content mt-10 mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-base-300">2. 目录与 templates 结构</h2>
      <p class="mb-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-base-content/90">主题采用标准 Baklib 主题目录。当前核心页面模板共 <strong>6 个</strong>（已移除旧版 <code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">index.help_center</code>、<code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">page.video</code> 等）。</p>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-base-content mt-6 mb-3">仓库目录概览</h3>
      <div class="not-prose overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full min-w-[640px] border-collapse text-left text-sm">
          <thead>
            <tr class="border-b border-base-300 bg-base-200/80 dark:border-base-300 dark:bg-base-300/50">
              <th class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-base-content">路径</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-base-content">说明</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-base-300 dark:divide-base-300">
            <tr><td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-xs">config/settings_schema.json</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-base-content/80">主题元数据、语言列表、站点级设置分组</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-xs">layout/</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-base-content/80">基础布局（<code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">theme.liquid</code>、<code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">error.liquid</code>）</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-xs">templates/</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-base-content/80">页面模板（见下表）</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-xs">snippets/</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-base-content/80">可复用片段（页头、页脚、侧栏、搜索列表、AI 搜索、页面工具等）</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-xs">locales/</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-base-content/80">运行时 UI 文案（<code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">*.json</code>）与编辑器标签（<code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">*.schema.json</code>）</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-xs">presets/</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-base-content/80">HTML 预设：<code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">header_menu_html.html</code>、<code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">footer_menu_html.html</code>、<code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">contact_html.html</code></td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-xs">src/</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-base-content/80">源码 CSS/JS（Tailwind v4、esbuild、Stimulus）</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-xs">assets/</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-base-content/80">编译产物、预览图（<code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">images/theme/&lt;lang&gt;/</code>、<code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">images/schema/</code>）</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-xs">statics/</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-base-content/80">静态自定义页（本页 <code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">about.liquid</code>、品牌规范 <code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">brand.liquid</code> 等）</td></tr>
          </tbody>
