      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-base-content mt-6 mb-3">辅助模板</h3>
      <ul class="mb-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-base leading-relaxed text-base-content/90">
        <li><code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">feedback_turbo_stream.liquid</code>、<code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">feedback_success_turbo_stream.liquid</code>、<code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">feedback_error_turbo_stream.liquid</code> — 读者反馈的 Turbo Stream 响应。</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-base-content mt-6 mb-3">首页模板选择</h3>
      <p class="mb-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-base-content/90">在 Baklib 站点编辑器中，将 Wiki 首页（<code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">index</code>）的模板切换为以下三者之一：</p>
      <ul class="mb-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-base leading-relaxed text-base-content/90">
        <li><strong>卡片式首页</strong>（<code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">index.card</code>）— 适合按栏目分区展示、视觉层次丰富的产品帮助中心。</li>
        <li><strong>常见问题中心</strong>（<code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">index.faqs</code>）— 适合 FAQ 为主、按分类 Tab 浏览的场景。</li>
        <li><strong>极简支持首页</strong>（<code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">index.support</code>）— 适合 Stripe/Intercom 风格的简洁支持门户。</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mb-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-base-content/90">三种首页均声明 <code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">sub_page_templates: ["page"]</code>，子页面统一使用 <code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">page.liquid</code>。</p>
    </section>

    <section id="settings-site">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-base-content mt-10 mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-base-300">3. 站点主题设置</h2>
      <p class="mb-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-base-content/90">以下设置在 Baklib 后台 <strong>主题设置</strong> 中配置，定义于 <code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">config/settings_schema.json</code>。站点创建并安装本主题后即可逐项填写。</p>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-base-content mt-6 mb-3">3.1 通用设置（generic）</h3>
      <div class="not-prose overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full min-w-[720px] border-collapse text-left text-sm">
          <thead>
            <tr class="border-b border-base-300 bg-base-200/80 dark:border-base-300 dark:bg-base-300/50">
              <th class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-base-content">设置 ID</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-base-content">类型</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-base-content">说明</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-base-content">默认值</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-base-300 dark:divide-base-300">
            <tr><td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-xs">logo_url</td><td class="px-4 py-3">图片</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-base-content/80">页头 Logo（3:1）。未设置时显示站点图标 + 名称</td><td class="px-4 py-3">—</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-xs">company_name</td><td class="px-4 py-3">文本</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-base-content/80">公司名称，显示在页脚</td><td class="px-4 py-3">Baklib.cn</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-xs">copyright_info</td><td class="px-4 py-3">文本</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-base-content/80">备案/版权信息</td><td class="px-4 py-3">All Rights Reserved</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-xs">show_published_at</td><td class="px-4 py-3">复选框</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-base-content/80">是否在内容页显示发布时间</td><td class="px-4 py-3">否</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-xs">show_author</td><td class="px-4 py-3">复选框</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-base-content/80">是否在内容页显示作者</td><td class="px-4 py-3">否</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-xs">ai_search_completed_text</td><td class="px-4 py-3">文本</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-base-content/80">AI 回答结束后的附加说明（覆盖默认结束语）</td><td class="px-4 py-3">—</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-xs">show_page_tools_dropdown</td><td class="px-4 py-3">复选框</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-base-content/80">是否在内容页显示「页面工具」下拉菜单（复制 Markdown、LLM 分享、MCP 等）</td><td class="px-4 py-3">是</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-base-content mt-6 mb-3">3.2 自定义 HTML（custom_html）</h3>
      <p class="mb-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-base-content/90">支持 HTML 标签与有限的 Tailwind CSS 类名。三项均提供 <code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">presets/</code> 预设，新建站点会自动填入示例内容，可按需修改。</p>
      <div class="not-prose overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full min-w-[720px] border-collapse text-left text-sm">
          <thead>
            <tr class="border-b border-base-300 bg-base-200/80 dark:border-base-300 dark:bg-base-300/50">
              <th class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-base-content">设置 ID</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-base-content">类型</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-base-content">说明</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-base-content">预设文件</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-base-300 dark:divide-base-300">
            <tr><td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-xs">head_html</td><td class="px-4 py-3">HTML</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-base-content/80">注入 <code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">&lt;head&gt;</code>，常用于统计代码、客服机器人等</td><td class="px-4 py-3">—</td></tr>
