      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-base-content mt-6 mb-3">6.1 支持的语言（7 种）</h3>
      <p class="mb-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-base-content/90">运行时 UI 与主题编辑器均提供以下语言包：</p>
      <p class="mb-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-base-content/90"><code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">en</code> · <code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">zh-CN</code> · <code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">zh-TW</code> · <code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">ko</code> · <code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">ja</code> · <code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">de</code> · <code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">fr</code></p>
      <p class="mb-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-base-content/90">新增语言时须同时维护 <code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">locales/&lt;locale&gt;.json</code>、<code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">locales/&lt;locale&gt;.schema.json</code>，并在 <code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">settings_schema.json → theme_info.theme_languages</code> 中注册。</p>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-base-content mt-6 mb-3">6.2 翻译键规范：不嵌入变量</h3>
      <p class="mb-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-base-content/90">翻译字符串<strong>不应内嵌 Liquid 变量或占位符片段</strong>。需要动态拼接的文案应拆分为多个键，在模板中组合。例如分页状态：</p>
      <ul class="mb-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-base leading-relaxed text-base-content/90">
        <li><code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">templates.page.pagination_status_prefix</code> — 「正在查看第 」</li>
        <li><code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">templates.page.pagination_status_middle</code> — 「 条，共 」</li>
        <li><code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">templates.page.pagination_status_suffix</code> — 「 条」</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mb-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-base-content/90">带参数的翻译（如 LLM 提示词）使用 Baklib 的 <code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">| t, url: ...</code> 过滤器传参，而非在 JSON 中写 Liquid。</p>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-base-content mt-6 mb-3">6.3 AI 搜索</h3>
      <ul class="mb-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-base leading-relaxed text-base-content/90">
        <li>需在 Baklib 站点层面开启 AI 搜索能力（<code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">site.ai_search_enabled?</code>）。</li>
        <li>搜索页（<code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">search.liquid</code>）右侧侧栏渲染 <code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">_support_ai_search</code> 片段；有搜索结果时自动展示并传入当前关键词。</li>
        <li>站点设置 <code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">ai_search_completed_text</code> 可自定义 AI 回答结束语；否则使用 <code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">locales/*/ai.completed</code> 默认文案。</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-base-content mt-6 mb-3">6.4 页面工具与 LLM 分享</h3>
      <ul class="mb-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-base leading-relaxed text-base-content/90">
        <li>由站点设置 <code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">show_page_tools_dropdown</code> 控制是否显示。</li>
        <li>提供：复制 Markdown、在 ChatGPT/Claude 中打开、复制 MCP 安装命令、连接 Cursor/VS Code。</li>
        <li>实现于 <code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">snippets/_page_tools_dropdown.liquid</code>，依赖 Stimulus 控制器 <code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">copy-page</code>、<code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">page-tools</code>。</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-base-content mt-6 mb-3">6.5 读者反馈</h3>
      <ul class="mb-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-base leading-relaxed text-base-content/90">
        <li>叶子页面（无子页面）底部展示反馈按钮（<code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">_feedback_button</code>）。</li>
        <li>提交后通过 Turbo Stream 模板异步更新 UI，无需整页刷新。</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-base-content mt-6 mb-3">6.6 侧栏导航（_aside_nav）</h3>
      <ul class="mb-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-base leading-relaxed text-base-content/90">
        <li>内容页、支持首页、搜索页共用右侧粘性侧栏。</li>
        <li>包含：常见主题链接（顶级栏目）、当前页标签云（如有）、联系支持（<code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">contact_html</code>）。</li>
        <li>卡片首页将 <code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">contact_html</code> 作为页面底部独立区块展示，而非侧栏。</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-base-content mt-6 mb-3">6.7 设计系统与颜色</h3>
      <ul class="mb-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-base leading-relaxed text-base-content/90">
        <li>模板样式使用 DaisyUI 语义类（<code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">bg-base-100</code>、<code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">text-base-content</code>、<code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">border-base-300</code>、<code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">text-primary</code> 等），避免硬编码 Hex 或 Tailwind 具名色阶。</li>
        <li>完整品牌 token 与组件示例见静态页 <a href="/s/brand" class="text-primary hover:underline">/s/brand</a>（<code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">statics/brand.liquid</code>）。</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-base-content mt-6 mb-3">6.8 预览图与主题卡片</h3>
      <p class="mb-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-base-content/90">按语言放置预览图至 <code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">assets/images/theme/&lt;lang&gt;/</code>：</p>
      <ul class="mb-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-base leading-relaxed text-base-content/90">
        <li><code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">thumb.png</code> — 主题选择器缩略图</li>
        <li><code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">index.png</code>、<code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">index-faqs.png</code>、<code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">index-card.png</code>、<code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">index-support.png</code>、<code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">page.png</code> — 预览截图</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mb-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-base-content/90">模板 schema 缩略图位于 <code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">assets/images/schema/</code>。<code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">settings_schema.json</code> 中 <code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">${lang}</code> 占位符会自动解析为当前管理员 UI 语言。</p>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-base-content mt-6 mb-3">6.9 已移除的旧模板</h3>
      <p class="mb-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-base-content/90">当前版本不再包含以下模板与片段，请勿引用：</p>
      <ul class="mb-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-base leading-relaxed text-base-content/90">
        <li><code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">index.help_center.liquid</code> — 旧版帮助中心首页</li>
        <li><code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">page.video.liquid</code> — 视频页面模板</li>
        <li><code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">_nav_tree.liquid</code>、<code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">_index_list_tree.liquid</code> 等旧导航树片段</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section id="dev">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-base-content mt-10 mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-base-300">7. 本地开发与构建</h2>
      <p class="mb-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-base-content/90">修改 <code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">src/</code> 下的 CSS 或 JS 后须重新构建，产物输出至 <code class="rounded bg-base-200 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-base-content dark:bg-base-300/50">assets/</code>。</p>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-base-content mt-6 mb-3">环境要求</h3>
      <ul class="mb-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-base leading-relaxed text-base-content/90">
        <li>Node.js（用于资源构建）</li>
        <li>Baklib Wiki 站点并安装本主题</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-base-content mt-6 mb-3">常用命令</h3>
      <pre class="mb-4 overflow-x-auto rounded-lg border border-base-300 bg-base-200/80 p-4 dark:bg-base-300/40"><code class="language-bash block font-mono text-sm leading-relaxed text-base-content">yarn install
yarn build    # 生产构建（CSS + JS）
yarn dev      # 开发模式，监听文件变更</code></pre>

      <p class="mb-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-base-content/90">可选：安装 Ruby Guard 实现浏览器 LiveReload（需 livereload 浏览器扩展）：</p>
      <pre class="mb-4 overflow-x-auto rounded-lg border border-base-300 bg-base-200/80 p-4 dark:bg-base-300/40"><code class="language-bash block font-mono text-sm leading-relaxed text-base-content">bundle install
bundle exec guard</code></pre>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-base-content mt-6 mb-3">技术栈摘要</h3>
      <ul class="mb-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-base leading-relaxed text-base-content/90">
        <li><strong>CSS</strong>：Tailwind CSS v4 + DaisyUI 5</li>
        <li><strong>JS</strong>：esbuild 打包；Hotwired Turbo + Stimulus；Alpine.js（折叠等交互）；Lucide 图标</li>
        <li><strong>模板</strong>：Liquid v2 语法；ProseMirror 友好 HTML 输出</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

